{
  "stem": "1641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't feel it so strongly but still very painful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they cut out a big piece of flesh from my left leg, which can be still seen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was about approximately 18 centimeters by 12 centimeters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He cut it out real deep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then when the cut was made, then he sprinkled a generous around of kerosene or petrol.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm not sure which one, one or the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was extremely-- I-- I fainted from the pain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then he put a bandage on, and they left the kerosene settle into the blood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And all night, I couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was terrible painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was, you know, moaning, like all the others were also moaning, so it was nothing special.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was horrible days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then every second day, he came back to everybody, checked the conditions, took temperatures.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In my case, I had to go up to him on one leg-- I couldn't stand on that leg, of course-- and then he had a look at it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He took-- he took out his Leica camera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He took snapshots.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He had already a-- a whole dossier with my photos on, how the pus develops, how this gets more and more swollen every day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then he put another dose of kerosene back on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So then he took another photo the next day and the day after.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it went on like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But after about three weeks-- could be three or it could be four weeks-- end of September, by that time, he finished.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He packed up all his files, his photos, and he finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "No more kerosene.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then the Jewish doctor, who was-- who remained there-- he-- he remained.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
